The paper discusses software engineering patterns for designing machine learning systems, which suggests that it belongs to the software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of mathematics and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in machine learning, as well as the need to address software complexity and quality in system design (cs.SY). Finally, the paper may also touch on distributed computing (cs.DC) as machine learning systems often require large amounts of data and computing power.
